OL,5,FHe said the case could have been
OL,6,Fsettled "a long time ago".
OL,8,FHe added: "The licence payers are
OL,9,Fgoing to pay for this . The BBC aren't
OL,10,Fusing their own money, Spotlight
OL,11,Faren't, the license fee payers are."
OL,13,FMr Adams said his thoughts were with
OL,14,Fthe family of Denis Donaldson.
OL,16,FA jury at the High Court in Dublin
OL,17,Ffound in his favour on Friday, after
OL,18,Fdetermining that was the meaning of
OL,19,Fwords included in the programme and
OL,20,Farticle.
