OL,5,FThey were tasked with determining
OL,6,Fwhether the words in the BBC spotlight
OL,7,Fprogramme and accompanying article, on
OL,8,Fwhich Mr Adams brought the complaint,
OL,9,Fmean that he sanctioned and approved
OL,10,Fthe murder of Mr Donaldson.
OL,12,FMr Owens said they were to consider
OL,13,Fwhether it was "more likely than not"
OL,14,Fthat a "hypothetical reasonable
OL,15,Freader" would take that meaning from
OL,16,Fthe words.
