OL,3,CGerry Adams wins libel case against BBC
OL,5,FThey returned with their verdict on
OL,6,FFriday after six hours and 49 minutes
OL,7,Fof deliberations in total.
OL,9,FMr Owens told the jury that the BBC
OL,10,Fhad put forward the position that Mr
OL,11,FAdams had "no reputation at all" and
OL,12,Fthe broadcaster had argued to the jury
OL,13,Fthat it should award only nominal
OL,14,Fdamages, putting forward the option of
OL,15,Fjust one euro.
OL,17,FMr Adams' team had argued that the
OL,18,Fdefamation fell within the "very
OL,19,Fserious" or "exceptional" end of the
OL,20,Fdamages scale.
